rComments: The actual course material was really interesting and since he's so passionate about the subject, he finds very interesting and memorable ways to explain course material. The course is memorization heavy so you have to study a lot, but the final is non-cumulative. labs are interesting and chill. had a group project that boosts your grade lots!

Great prof, very passionate and knowledgeable about what he teaches, and always encourages students to ask questions. This course is memorization heavy, but the final is non-cumulative. The labs are chill, and interesting, however, they run every single week.
